blog.title: THE COLLECTIVE WORK OF CHAR + SAM
blog.description: C H A R  +  S A M

body:
Wow. It’s been a good bit of 4 months since we’ve posted last! It was a whirlwind for the both of us as 2018 came to an end. There were plenty of changes happening…the main one being that one of us moved from one city to another. It was a stressful time but 2019 was already looking promising and we’re happy to finally let the dust settle! 

What have we been up to since the start of the year? Our biggest mention is our YouTube Channel! As a New Years resolution we decided to act on something that has been in the talks for a while…with the push from our dear friend, Megan, we finally did it. We have yet to miss a week without an upload and are super proud of it. We hope to continually grow as a business. We already know how cringey we will be when we look back at our first episodes haha! 

We’ve already had a handful of photoshoots…from headshots to engagements, but we’re super stoked we already have 5 weddings in our near future! We also just got back from our first trip of the year to New Orleans! We had booked a couple shoots out there and decided to extend the trip and make it something we’d actually enjoy. Our highlights were the airboat tours to see some alligators and getting our dope tattoos! 

In the meantime, stick with us on Instagram as well as YouTube to keep up with our daily lives <3
